18#include "lib.h"
19#include "toolcontext.h"
20#include "segtype.h"
21
22struct segment_type *get_segtype_from_string(struct cmd_context *cmd,
23 const char *str)
24{
25 struct segment_type *segtype;
26
27 dm_list_iterate_items(segtype, &cmd->segtypes) {
28 if (!strcmp(segtype->name, str))
29 return segtype;
30 }
31
32 if (!(segtype = init_unknown_segtype(cmd, str)))
33 return_NULL;
34
35 segtype->library = NULL;
36 dm_list_add(&cmd->segtypes, &segtype->list);
37 log_warn("WARNING: Unrecognised segment type %s", str);
38 return segtype;
39}
